    General Stores in Colaba, Mumbai

    (350 Ratings & Reviews) 4.1 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Colaba, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Colaba, Mumbai from the list given above.
